<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.2.7">
<l>taḻa miṉṟimun nīraiyañ ñāṉṟu takainta tēkaṇṭu vañcinuṇ maruṅkul</l>
<l>māḻai māṉmaṭa nōkkiyai viṭṭu vāḻkil lāmati yilmaṉat tāṉai</l>
<l>yēḻai yaiyilaṅ kaikkiṟai taṉṉai yeṅka ḷaiyoḻi yakkolai yavaṉai</l>
<l>cūḻu māniṉai māmaṇi vaṇṇā colli ṉōmtaṭam poṅkattam poṅkō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Jewel-hued [lord], think of the way [you] will plot death, except for us,</l>
<l>For the leader of Laṅkā, the fool, the one who, having seen that day</l>
<l rend="indent">the blocking of the restless, three-watered [sea],</l>
<l>With an undiscerning mind, was not able to live, abandoning the one</l>
<l rend="indent">with an innocent, doe[-eyed], simple gaze</l>
<l>And creeper[-like] thin waist. We say, “Oh, it’s a turbulent road;</l>
<l rend="indent">it’s a turbulent path!"</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
